text: holy fucking shit

>>> My name is Brian Canada, I am on a mission to build/have every EDH deck possible. Meaning I am building a deck of every legal legendary creature. Almost 2 years ago I started a YouTube channel documenting my quest, as I understand it, no one has ever done this as it is believed to be impossible. I try to build decks that are fun and different. Currently I just finished building deck#325 - Xantcha, trying to stay current when possible. My channel (Cure for the Common Game) is growing every day currently sitting at 1,360 subscribers.
